lead_paragraph: D'Angelo Russell knows he must rebuild the Los Angeles Lakers' trust in him after the rookie guard's unflattering video exchange with teammate Nick Young ended up on social media.

headline.print_headline: Russell Apologizes for Taking Video of Lakers Teammate Young
